a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/platee-rameau/" rel="tag">Plate. Rameau</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rebecca-von-lipinski/" rel="tag">Rebecca von Lipinski</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/reinhard-traub/" rel="tag">Reinhard Traub</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/shigeo-ishino/" rel="tag">Shigeo Ishino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/staatsoper-stuttgart/" rel="tag">Staatsoper Stuttgart</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/susanne-gschwender/" rel="tag">Susanne Gschwender</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/thomas-walker/" rel="tag">Thomas Walker</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Andr Morsch, Anna Eiermann, Calixto Bieito, Christian Curnyn, Cyril Auvity, Opera lirica, Plate. Rameau, Rebecca von Lipinski, Reinhard Traub, Shigeo Ishino, Staatsoper Stuttgart, Susanne Gschwender, Thomas Walker"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e15610f34674f02caf174515ea5136d4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Mussomeli1-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Gianguido Mussomeli" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Gianguido Mussomeli"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/gianguido-mussomeli/">View all articles by Gianguido Mussomeli</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav